{"tid":1027964,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[勇士] 郭卓堅入稟求減每日單程證配額","createTime":"2019-02-19T07:08:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-19T07:33:54.000Z","uid":77196,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"6551971f60d7c8f3fc4b6fe4323072eb085f3c5b","tid":1027964,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T07:08:06.000Z","msg":"長洲居民郭卓堅入稟高等法院，指行政長官林鄭月娥行政失當，未有設法控制新移民來港的人數，今日到高等法院入稟申請司法覆核，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>要求法庭頒令特首需嚴格執行《基本法》第22條，減少單程證數目，以配合香港的承擔能力</strong></span>。<br />\n<br />\n郭卓堅表示，是次申請司法覆核是迫不得己，因本港人口膨漲問題嚴重，每日持單程證本港的人數是由中央徵求特首意見後再確定，現時本港的公共資源供不應求，當局應該減少或撤消單程證名額，待有勞動力需求時才重新發放。"},{"pid":"9414577566f8fec7e8a3dc7f603c5bb32eb90b82","tid":1027964,"uid":33028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T07:09:56.000Z","msg":"佢有邊次司法覆核係贏?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"625a7a206fededdd5b4892d3dae44ff79df31e9b","tid":1027964,"uid":77196,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9414577566f8fec7e8a3dc7f603c5bb32eb90b82","tid":1027964,"uid":33028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T07:09:56.000Z","msg":"佢有邊次司法覆核係贏?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T07:16:23.000Z","msg":"長洲無牌殯儀案 覆核勝訴<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20150228/19058084\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20150228%2F19058084&d=XUHW2qJizO2pFN7N4VPpEjvkInyplymEwWc8t9jwBTE%3D&h=8fb7693e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20150228%2F19058084&h=f2a73a65\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20150228/19058084</a>"},{"pid":"ac98014f5e7b7a19d1db53248366dc36d36f4659","tid":1027964,"uid":73804,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T07:33:54.000Z","msg":"1989年到北京聲援學運，6月7日他在北京被帶到上海公安招待所軟禁一年，幾經波折才回到香港。港英政府後來知道他被中共軟禁，給予他居英權，更曾建議他離開香港，但他沒有想過移民。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}